Package: patdatatools
Type: Package
Title: Calculation of types of complexity and aggregated indices at the level of spatial units
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tom Broekel
Maintainer: The package maintainer <tobroworks@icloud.com>
Description: The package features functions to calculate indices approximating technological complexity using patent data.
    It also contains functions of aggregating these indices at the country and regional level.
